This is the way we are performing for returns.js .
FIrstly we write the test cases for below mentioned cases and develop code.

POST/api/returns  {customerId, movieId}

- return 401 if client not logged in
- return 400 if customerId not provided
- return 400 if movieId not provided
- return 404 if no rental found for this customer/movie
- return 400 if rental already processed
- return 200 if valid request

-set the rental date
-calculate rental fee
-increase the stock
-return the rental